            <h1 class="hide-on-mobile hide-on-tablet">Overview of the Norwegian Earth System Model (NorESM2) and key climate response of CMIP6 DECK, historical, and scenario simulations</h1>
            <div class="hide-on-desktop h1">Overview of the Norwegian Earth System Model (NorESM2) and key climate response of CMIP6 DECK, historical, and scenario simulations</div>
